captions.translation: [JIUTAI] Along the edge of the blade are beaten traces
"Clustering Clouds of Heaven", it will be!

captions.transcription: futatsu no mei no mitsurugi nite.

captions.translation: It will rule the land to the four seas,
celebrate the abundance of the five staple crops.
captions.transcription: go-koku jōju mo kono toki nare ya.

captions.translation: "I, before you, as the deity of your clan:
captions.transcription: Sunawachi nanji ga uji no shin

captions.translation: the manifestation of Inari: the Little Fox,
come to aid you in fulfilling your task.
Now, I am done!" So saying, takes his leave.
Once more he leaps upon the mass of clouds,
Again, more he leaps upon the mass of clouds,
and return to Higashiyama, the eastern mountains, the peak of Mt. Inari!
captions.transcription: Higashiyama Inari no mine ni zo kaerikeru.
